        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> Multiply every term by (x−1): the 1 becomes 1·(x−1) = x−1.<div class='fb-work'>4 + x − 1 = 6 → x = 3</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-1" onclick="check(1,'A')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="q-panel " id="qp-2">
