      <span class="math-eq">2/x + 3/(x + 2)</span>
      <div class="hint">LCD = x(x+2). Convert: 2/x → 2(x+2)/[x(x+2)] and 3/(x+2) → 3x/[x(x+2)]. Add numerators.</div>
    </div>
