      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-ok"><strong>Correct! 9x²</strong><div class='fb-work'>27^(2/3) = (∛27)² = 3² = 9<br>(x³)^(2/3) = x^(3·2/3) = x² <br>Result: 9x² ✓</div></div>
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> Apply the exponent to each factor separately. 27^(2/3) = (∛27)² = 9. (x³)^(2/3) = x².<div class='fb-work'>9 · x² = 9x²</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-0" onclick="check(0,'A')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><div class="q-panel " id="qp-1">
  <div class="math-layout">
