        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> In x^(m/n): denominator n = root, numerator m = power. x^(3/2) → square root (denominator 2), cubed (numerator 3) → (√x)³ = √(x³).<div class='fb-work'>x^(3/2) = √(x³)</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-1" onclick="check(1,'B')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
