        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(0,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>30 hours</div>
      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-ok"><strong>Correct! 3 hours</strong><div class="fb-work">Time = 45,000 liters ÷ 250 liters/min = 180 minutes<br>Convert to hours: 180 min × (1 hr / 60 min) = 3 hours ✓</div></div>
