      <div class="problem-text">A printer prints 40 pages per minute. Each page uses 0.5 grams of ink. Ink cartridges hold 120 grams each.</div>
      <div class="hint">Chain the rates: pages/min × grams/page = grams/min. Then find how many minutes one cartridge lasts: 120 grams ÷ (grams/min).</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 2 · Chained Rates</div>
      <div class="q-text">How many <strong>minutes</strong> does one ink cartridge last?</div>
      <div class="opts" id="opts-1">
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'A')"><span class="opt-l">A</span>3 minutes</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'B')"><span class="opt-l">B</span>6 minutes</div>
