        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> Chain the rates: 40 pages/min × 0.5 grams/page = 20 grams/min. Then divide the cartridge capacity by the rate.<div class="fb-work">120 grams ÷ 20 grams/min = 6 minutes</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-1" onclick="check(1,'B')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
