        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> "Given that they studied" means restrict to the Studied row only. Of 70 students who studied, 56 passed. Use 70 as the denominator — not 100.<div class="fb-work">56 (studied and passed) / 70 (total who studied) = 56/70</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-1" onclick="check(1,'C')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
