      <span class="math-eq">y ≥ −x + 5</span>
      <div class="hint-box">To find which point lies in the solution region, substitute each answer choice into both inequalities. The correct point must satisfy both simultaneously.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 1 · Testing Points</div>
