      <div class="panel-label">Problem</div>
      <div class="problem-text">In the xy-plane, the point (k, 4) lies in the solution region of the following system:</div>
      <span class="math-eq">2x − y &gt; 3</span>
      <span class="math-eq">x + 2y ≤ 14</span>
      <div class="hint-box">Substitute (k, 4) into both inequalities and find the range of k-values that satisfy both simultaneously.</div>
    </div>
