        <div class="feedback" id="fb-2-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> Solve |f − 500| ≤ 8 as a compound inequality. The ≤ sign means the boundaries are included — a fill of exactly 492 or 508 is still within tolerance.<div class="fb-work">−8 ≤ f − 500 ≤ 8 → 492 ≤ f ≤ 508</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-2" onclick="check(2,'C')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
